snippet.title: Shinsekai: Into the Depths - Launch Trailer | Nintendo Switch | Apple Arcade
snippet.description:
Take a deep breath and start your journey of survival and deep-sea exploration in Shinsekai: Into the Depths!

Available now on #NintendoSwitch alongside a free update to the #AppleArcade version. 🐟 http://bit.ly/ShinsekaiIntoTheDepths
